show.description: Ek ladki jisne apni zindagi apne pyar se shadi karne mein laga di, aaj usi ke ghar mein naukar banke jeene ko majboor hai. Izzat, asli rishta aur ek pote ki ek jhalak — yeh kahani dil tod degi. Kya ek ladki ki pehchaan sirf zarurat ke waqt yaad aati hai? Abhi dekhna shuru kijiye.
